+
+RENDER COMMAND — ALL OPTIONS
+-----------------------------
+
+  box3d render --profile <name> [options]
+
+  REQUIRED
+    -p, --profile <name>       Profile to use (mvs | arcade | dvd | custom)
+
+  INPUT / OUTPUT
